    items={[
      {
        title: 'Robust Construction',
        description:
          'The crusher is built with a strong shaft and frame, engineered to withstand long hours of operation without compromising performance.',
        icon: 'tabler:layers-union',
      },
      {
        title: 'High Capacity',
        description: `With an impressive throughput of 3 tons per hour, this machine is capable of handling large volumes of plastic waste, making it suitable for both medium and large-scale recycling facilities.`,
        icon: 'tabler:artboard',
      },
      {
        title: 'Patented Technology',
        description:
          `The 1600 Type is equipped with patented features that set it apart in the market, ensuring you're investing in cutting-edge technology.`,
        icon: 'tabler:writing',
      },
      {
        title: 'Multiple Sets of Blades',
        description: `The machine comes with 16 rotating blades and 4 fixed blades, designed for a more efficient and thorough crushing process.`,
        icon: 'tabler:podium',
      },
      {
        title: 'Enhanced Design',
        description: `It includes knife heads on both sides, a thickened base, and a thickened steel plate for added strength and durability.`,
        icon: 'tabler:rocket',
      },
      {
        title: 'Rotor Diameter and Blade Frame Length',
        description: `The crusher has an 880mm rotor diameter and a 1700mm blade frame length, which contributes to its high capacity and efficiency.`,
        icon: 'tabler:eyeglass',
      },
    ]}
  />

